{"type": "article", "id": 29766, "title": "项链式耳机", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-18T22:47:27Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 39, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160718182342pMDGfes6q203T7l8.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>还记得我们之前介绍过的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/28587.html\">骨传导耳机/太阳眼镜</a>吗？今天要介绍的 Necksound 项链式耳机和它使用了相似的科技，专门为喜欢在运动时听音乐的人打造。它内置一个可以调节的吸附系统，通过磁铁能够紧密地贴合在衣服上，而且使用由防水和防尘的材料打造，不用担心大汗淋漓会影响它工作。戴上后你可以同时听到音乐和外界的声音，可以避免在运动时发生意外。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1892029779/necksound-smart-wireless-necklace-wearable-music-d\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，早鸟价为 90 欧元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718182352GT5QSNoyYtAmWibd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.455752\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607181823528xQXiDuhJCkKLtFf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.660294\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607181823525X8P1bVKcNpsdOE7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561765\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718182352yNAP8IDkRLBCvmg5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.398529\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}